data.description: Exquisite elegance perched on a bigger lot with side yard access for your recreational vehicles. Be graciously greeted by a gated courtyard with beautiful ironwork and 3 garage spaces. As you embark inside you will appreciate the crown molding, custom mural artwork, soaring ceilings, alluring full bar area, with pendant lighting, seating, granite and amenities. Each bedroom is equipped with its own full bath, exquisitely painted with lavish textures and colors. Truly an entertainer's dream, offering luxury kitchen with Wolf Brand appliances including warming tray,granite, and lots of cabinet and counter space & Subzero fridge.Escape to the theater, fully wired  surround sound and ambiance lighting.Vast owners suite with sitting area, double faced fireplace, exquisite bath and vanity area.
